Record Class UnaryPair<T>

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
pegasus.tuple.UnaryPair<T>
Type Parameters:

Record Components:
a - The first object
b - The second object
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<T>, BaseTuple<T>, Tuple<T>, IndexedIterable<T>
public record UnaryPair<T>(T a, T b) extends Record implements Tuple<T>
A pair of objects of the same type.
